(6668, 1, '2015-02-10 06:04:44', '2015-02-10 06:04:44', '<p class="testing_text">\r\n콘크릿은 \r\n<strong>테스팅 전략 수립부터\r\n결과에 따른 전문가 의견 제공까지</strong>\r\n모든 과정을 함께합니다.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n[tagline]테스팅 서비스 범위[/tagline]<p>콘크릿은 다양한 용도의 SW 테스팅이 가능합니다</p>\r\n\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<div class="testing_area">\r\n<img src="http://conkrit.com:8080/wp/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/testing_area_icon1.gif" alt="-" width="88" height="85" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-6550" />\r\n<h3>PC</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<div class="testing_area">\r\n<img src="http://conkrit.com:8080/wp/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/testing_area_icon2.gif" alt="testing_area_icon2" width="54" height="85" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-6551" />\r\n<h3>APP</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[one_fourth]\r\n<div class="testing_area">\r\n<img src="http://conkrit.com:8080/wp/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/testing_area_icon3.gif" alt="testing_area_icon3" width="112" height="85" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-6552" />\r\n<h3>WEB</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n[/one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[one_fourth_last]\r\n<div class="testing_area">\r\n<img src="http://conkrit.com:8080/wp/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/testing_area_icon4_2.gif" alt="testing_area_icon4_2" width="138" height="85" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-6667" />\r\n<h3>IOT</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n[/one_fourth_last]\r\n\r\n<div class="testing_kind_title">[tagline]테스팅 서비스 종류[/tagline]<p>콘크릿은 당신의 SW를 위한 모든 테스트를 제공합니다</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<ul class="testing_kind_wrap">\r\n<li class="testing_kind">\r\n<a href="/wp/?page_id=6594"> <img src="http://conkrit.com:8080/wp/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/testing_kind_functional_bg.png" alt="-" width="286" height="328" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-6579" /> <img src="http://conkrit.com:8080/wp/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/testing_kind_functional_over.png" alt="-" width="286" height="328" class="overlay alignnone size-full wp-image-6555" /> <img src="http://conkrit.com:8080/wp/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/testing_kind_functional_text.png" alt="functional testing" width="286" height="328" class="text alignnone size-full wp-image-6573" /> </a>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class="testing_kind">\r\n<a href="/wp/?page_id=6596"> <img src="http://conkrit.com:8080/wp/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/testing_kind_usability_bg.png" alt="-" width="286" height="328" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-6580" /> <img src="http://conkrit.com:8080/wp/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/testing_kind_usability_over.png" alt="-" width="286" height="328" class="overlay alignnone size-full wp-image-6558" /> <img src="http://conkrit.com:8080/wp/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/testing_kind_usability_text.png" alt="usability testing" width="286" height="328" class="text alignnone size-full wp-image-6574" /> </a>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class="testing_kind">\r\n<a href="/wp/?page_id=6598"> <img src="http://conkrit.com:8080/wp/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/testing_kind_global_bg.png" alt="-" width="286" height="328" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-6581" /> <img src="http://conkrit.com:8080/wp/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/testing_kind_global_over.png" alt="-" width="286" height="328" class="overlay alignnone size-full wp-image-6561" /> <img src="http://conkrit.com:8080/wp/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/testing_kind_global_text.png" alt="globalization testing" width="286" height="328" class="text alignnone size-full wp-image-6575" /> </a>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class="testing_kind performance">\r\n<a href="/wp/?page_id=6600"> <img src="http://conkrit.com:8080/wp/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/testing_kind_performance_bg.png" alt="-" width="286" height="328" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-6582" /> <img src="http://conkrit.com:8080/wp/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/testing_kind_performance_over.png" alt="-" width="286" height="328" class="overlay alignnone size-full wp-image-6564" /> <img src="http://conkrit.com:8080/wp/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/testing_kind_performance_text.png" alt="performance testing" width="286" height="328" class="text alignnone size-full wp-image-6